No LoRA adapters bundled in v22 synapse-app. The retrieve-expand adapter
was retired after the 2026-04-26 PoC showed the v3 system prompt + base
Gemma 4 E2B matched or outperformed it (REPORT-20260426-SYN-adapter-
removal-h1.md). The hot-swap infrastructure in
lib/src/llm/llamadart_backend.dart is preserved so reuse apps (e.g.
gabjil-extract) can drop their own GGUFs here and register them via
EngineConfig.adapters.
